headline: 3 Reliable Dividend Stocks Offering At Least 4.2% Yield
summary: The United States market has experienced a positive trend, rising 7.1% over the last week and 7.7% over the past year, with earnings expected to grow by 14% annually. In this environment, reliable dividend stocks offering yields of at least 4.2% can be appealing for investors seeking steady income alongside potential capital appreciation.
